data.description: Discover the tranquility of Escondido in this inviting 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom condo nestled in the community of Felicita Villas. A perfect blend of comfort and sophistication, this home offers a serene escape from the hustle and bustle. Step inside to find a spacious, well-lit living area, ideal for both relaxation and hosting guests. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and generous counter space, creating a delightful space for culinary endeavors. The primary bedroom, complete with ensuite bathroom, provides a private retreat with a balcony. Felicita Villas offers a variety of amenities where you can spend a leisurely weekend by the pool, indulge in the soothing waters of the spa, or simply enjoy creating cherished memories with loved ones in this well-kept community. Conveniently situated near local amenities, parks, and schools with ample guest parking available, this condo offers the   perfect balance of peaceful suburban living. Don’t miss the chance to make this property your own!
